{
  "texts": [
    "Omeroglu et al.",
    "[53] proposed a network consisting of multiple branches and a hybrid integration of feature maps from multiple modalities.",
    "These branches allow us to dissect multimodal interactions and draw out specific details.",
    "A soft attention module, a tweaked Xception architecture, and a specialized feature extraction method all work together to train the network to focus on individual skin lesions.",
    "The suggested framework was evaluated using a sevenpoint dataset that is accessible to the public."
  ]
}